title: honor help?
body:
Hi i noticed that alot of my friends already got the icon and despite the fact they played for maybe about a year when i have since around season 2 i have yet to get it, where as they had it about the same time you came out with the icons. i had about maybe 3 different ribbons since my time but slowly lost them over time prob to reports.

Am i still going to get any icon if i didnt end with the season with a ribbon despite having 3 different ribbons with the mass amount of time i put into this game? (i noticed it said (this should be wrapped by September 30) and so i was getting curious if i ever was going to get one) 

Thanks

replies.body: No worries yet, just as you mentioned those icons are still going out and should be finished by 9/30!
oh im sorry i just realized its by next month and not this one thanks sorry again
